“Nothing, really”

"What?" Augustin frowns like you've said something offensive. "No, $mc, we can't accept that. If you won't take coin then at least— At least, let us give you something to eat."

You open your mouth to decline.

Well. You can't really say no to that, can you? Those awful morning clothes will just have to wait a little longer.
 
