:: Lou {"position":"6700,350","size":"100,100"}
[You are deep in a relationship with Lou, and she is aware of you being a werewolf]

"Is your back sore again?"

It is scary how well Lou reads you after all this time. You haven't seen each other in a week and yet she picked on all the signals. She's been busy prepping for the next festival and you ? Well, you're experiencing some pre moon symptoms. 

The lie is almost at the tip of your tongue before you get a look on Lou's face and close your mouth. You've never quite realised how much you lie about these kinds of things. It's sad really, you used to tell everything to your grandma, but with her death, a part of you got sealed away with her. Hiding. Until now, that is.
She knows the full moon is in a few days and she knows werewolves tend to get all sorts of symptoms like back pain and sore muscles. Hells, one time you even blocked your neck for three days until the Moon magically healed you up.

She doesn't look at you with pity though, nor with fear, which you expected in the beginning. No, she's looking at you in a way that makes you feel raw, vulnerable. 
And all too tingly inside. 

You can't help but look away. Her gaze is too difficult to bear, too sharp. You hear her footsteps echo on the wood, and see her get closer to you. You feel her hand on your shoulder. You meet her eyes, curious.

"Come with me, love"

Lou's been pretty busy the past few weeks, mostly preparing for the festival and making sure that the inn will run smoothly. Between her schedule and you feeling the effect of the full moon, you haven't seen her much in the past week.
As you climb the stairs, you can't help but realise how often she comes at your house and how little you get to her own room. But as you expect her to lead you to her place she turns on a right door, unlock it and open it, and enters leaving the door open for you to follow.
You've never seen this place before.
Its a bathtub, a huge wooden bathtub in the middle of a room, with a chest of drawers in the corner and an already lit fireplace. 

"I did not know you had a bathtub" you frown.

She smiles apologetically as she put another log in the fireplace. Which feels entirely unnecessary with how warm this place is compared to the rest of the inn. But you assume she does so to keep herself busy.

"Yes. Back when Auntie was there we used to do a bath service for anyone willing to pay. I was often the one doing it. After she died… Well it became too difficult to do that activity as well"
She pauses and then gives you a knowing smile, although it feels a little evasive to you. "Still make use of it often. Mostly to indulge in a proper bath... or if a customer is willing to pay more."

You hum. It makes sense. Two people working in an inn was probably easier to deal with and to add other services as well.
You pause though, and can't help the wicked smile that comes on your lips. Mostly because, while you got used to being nude, you can't help but feel slightly awkward in front of her.

"Is this your way of getting me naked?"
 
She laughs and oh, you wish you could hear it again. You adore how her eyes wrinkles when she smiles, the small dimple in her left cheek. How happy and free she looks right now.

"Please," she steps close to you, close enough that you can feel her own breath on your skin, noses almost touching.
"I can get you naked whenever I want to" she says gently grabbing the front of your shirt and fiddling with the button at the top. She looks down and stops before looking up, silently asking for consent. One you give with a nod.

"Is that a challenge?" You ask, cocking your head on the side. 

"Do you want it to be one?" She grins

Oh, you love how she's looking at you right now. Like for once the roles are reversed.
 You're the prey, and if she could she would eat you alive. 
She kisses you gently at the corner of your jaw and begins working on your clothes silently.

Its funny how vulnerable this moment is, and you watches as she, ever so tenderly, helps you get out of your clothes, folding them neatly all the while preparing a bath. She does it like she's done it a million times. And she probably did

As you settle into the bathtub you realise how much you missed this. The gentle comfort of the warm water against your sore muscles. Usually when you get back pain they can get so intense that doing an activity like warming water for yourself feels impossible.
You can't help the content sigh that escape you, as you close your eyes savouring every instant.
You feel warm lips against your forehead, and when you open you see Lou's gentle smile.

"I love seeing you like this."

"What, wet and naked?" You ask, a mischievous grin setting easily on your face.

It does get a small laugh out of her, which makes you smile triumphantly.

"No, silly." she boops your nose, then kisses your forehead again, "Happy."

Again Lou always had that talent to render you speechless. It's not uncomfortable though, so again, you chose to make a joke out of it. You lightly splash her.

 "There's enough space for both of us my love"

She smiles, that sweet little smile that she reserves just for you. Not the polished one she uses on clients.

"I'll join i promise I just need to make sure your water stays warm and –"

You cut her off, catching her hand in both of yours. You press a kiss to each fingertip, slow and deliberate, watching her expression shift with every single one. 

"Please stay."

Lou is a busy woman, a people pleaser often running everywhere making sure her business blooms and that everyone around her is satisfied and content. She doesnt stay with you as much time as she'd like that you know. But she misses you, you can see it in her eyes and her lingering touches. And so, this time, she does stay.


