:: home1 {"position":"1575,450","size":"100,100"}
	//Home,// you think tenderly.
    
It's nothing too big, just a small cabin, away from the center village, on the edge of the woods. You’ve built it with the help of the villagers.
	At first you thought the villager took pity, but now that you know them, they were simply their usual self; kind. Which came at a surprise at first. Honestly when you first moved to Tierce-Lieux, a few years back, you expected them to be like in any village; to be distrustful, finding new comers untrustworthy. They were the opposite; very welcoming, helping you on the very first day, bringing you dinner, fresh vegetables and baked goods. Even blankets and fresh clothes, which was quite needed as it was the middle of winter. Old Martin helped you with the roof, Germain with the windows, and Louise with the furniture.

	So despite what happened last night, it's with a smile that you reach your home. You slip around to the back, into the garden you consistently fail to take care of, and crouch down beside the small flower bed Lou put in for you. For good luck, she'd said, in the tone she uses when she's decided something and isn't taking arguments. She'd named the whole bed Elbert. You're still not sure why you should name a plant, but Lou was very insistent about it so you caved. 
	You dig around near the edge until your fingers touch cold metal and you take out the spare key. The bed looks a little neglected, you notice. A few of the flowers drooping. You pick off a bug making itself at home on one of the leaves. Lou would absolutely have your head if she saw the state of it.
Key in hand, you straighten up, absently scratching at your legs, and unlock the back door. The door closes behind you.

	//Finally//
    
    	Home is how you left it, although a bit messier because you genuinely forgot last night was the full moon which means you had to leave in a bit of a hurry. Well nonetheless you can now get out of those awful clothes.

[[You draw a warm bath.|warmbath]] 
[[You draw a cold bath.|coldbath]]


