:: woodclothes {"position":"1325,450","size":"100,100"}
<<if $height == "very small">>
	The shirt is way too big for your petite frame, the sleeves are so long that if you’re just  standing there, they almost reach below your knees. It looks like you’re wearing a robe. You feel like a child again, wearing your parent’s clothes. The fabric of the pants is itchy and covered in unknown stains. 
    But the outfit does the job, so you can't really complain about that. You can't help but feel a little worried at the prospect of walking barefoot and naked in the snow this winter, but maybe by then, you'll be a normal werewolf, in control of its form.
<<elseif $height == "small">>
	The shirt is too big for your frame, its sleeves slightly longer, reaching the tip of your fingertips.  and the fabric of the pants is itchy and covered in unknown stains. But it does the job, so you can't really complain. You can't help but feel a little worried at the prospect of walking barefoot and naked in the snow this winter, but maybe by then, you'll be a normal werewolf, in control of its form.
<<elseif $height == "tall">>
	The shirt is too small for your frame, its sleeves slightly shorter, reaching a bit before your wrists. The base of the shirt is also a bit short, pretty sure that if you raised both arms it would reach your navel. The fabric of the pants is itchy and covered in unknown stains.
 But it does the job, so you can't really complain. You can't help but feel a little worried at the prospect of walking barefoot and naked in the snow this winter, but maybe by then, you'll be a normal werewolf, in control of its form.
<<elseif $height == "very tall">>
	The shirt is way too small for your frame, its sleeves reaching the middle of your forearm, the base of your shirt at your belly button. You feel constricted, and you’re pretty sure that if you do any sudden movement the shirt will burst open. You must look ridiculous. You try to tug at the helm to make sure it's not too tight around your neck. The fabric of the pants is itchy too. 
    For a split second you almost want to take it all off but you can't risk having anyone see you naked, muddy and bloody running through the woods. You exhale. It's uncomfortable, sure but it does the job, so you can't really complain. You can't help but feel a little worried at the prospect of walking barefoot and naked in the snow this winter, but maybe by then, you'll be a normal werewolf, in control of its form.
<<else>>
